heading.summary: Blessed are they who keep the commandments.Ponder the precepts and ways of the Lord.O Lord, open our eyes, that we may behold wondrous things out of Thy law.O Lord, grant us Thy law, and make us to understand Thy precepts.O Lord, teach us Thy statutes, Thy law, and Thy commandments.O Lord, give us mercy, truth, and salvation.The Lord’s statutes and judgments comfort us during our pilgrimage.Make faithful people our companions.O Lord, teach us Thy statutes.O Lord, let Thy tender mercies come upon us.All the Lord’s commandments are faithful.O Lord, save us, for we have sought Thy precepts.The Lord’s law and His testimonies should be our meditation all the day.The Lord’s word is a lamp unto our feet.Depart from evildoers and keep the commandments of God.O Lord, we are Thy servants; give us understanding.The Lord’s testimonies are wonderful.The Lord’s law is the truth.O Lord, hear the voice of Thy servants according to Thy loving kindness.Great are Thy tender mercies, O Lord.Those who love the Lord’s law have peace.All the Lord’s commandments are righteousness.
